Director Wu.

15
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,440
Good day, madam.

16
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:49,280
I'm Wu Bingxiang, director of the Metropolitan Police Department.

17
00:00:47,279 --> 00:00:49,645
[Wu Bingxiang, Director of the Metropolitan Police Department]

18
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:51,040
Hello, Director Wu.

19
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:54,320
Come into the house with your mother.

20
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,320
I just walked into the door,

21
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,680
didn't even put my suitcase down,

22
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,200
and you are here already.

23
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,440
How efficient your people work.

24
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,440
Professor Chen, you left Beijing without permission.

25
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,560
Then you made a scene in Wuhan.

26
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,560
Now that you finally came back to Beijing.

27
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,040
How can I not pay a visit?

28
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,640
Director Wu is very kind.

29
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:20,400
Professor Chen, we are fellow villagers.

30
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:23,840
Naturally, I should take more care of you.

31
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:28,400
Don't forget that I was a sponsor when you got out of prison.

32
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,400
I'm involved here.

33
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:31,680
Clear.

34
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,280
Director Wu.

35
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,240
Have a seat in the house.

36
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,440
No, no, no.

37
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:37,280
He just came back.

38
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,280
Professor Chen.

39
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,480
Please behave yourself.

40
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,560
I will see you again.

41
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,280
Good bye.

42
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,520
Good bye.

43
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,160
A policeman came looking for you yesterday as well.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,680
Now you just arrived,

45
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,280
Wu Bingxiang were right after you.

46
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,440
Is something wrong?

47
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,360
They must have read it in the newspaper,

48
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,120
the report about my speech in Wuhan.

49
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,880
Don't bother sort out my stuff.

50
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,480
I'll go directly to Shizhi's place.

51
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,720
Okay.

52
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:39,760
Make way!

53
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,040
Make way! Make way!

54
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,240
Make way!

55
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:46,880
Make way!

56
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,320
Make way!

57
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,280
Make way!

58
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,120
Shizhi.

59
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:20,480
My brother.

60
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,240
Come in and warm up.

61
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,240
Brother Zhongfu, you're back.

62
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,440
Can you do me a favor.

63
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:30,080
Can you go next door and get Gao Yihan for me.

64
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,800
Tell him to bring Shouchang and Deqian.

65
00:03:33,174 --> 00:03:36,075
[Hu Shi, styled Shizhi, Professor at Peking University]

66
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:36,160
Better call Yucai, too.

67
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,000
Okay, I'm going now.

68
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:46,160
Brother Zhongfu, what happened?

69
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:51,440
Come. Having all these people here in this cold weather.

70
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,480
Excuse me.

71
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,520
Take a seat.

72
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,840
I invited you all here today

73
00:04:02,714 --> 00:04:04,297
[Li Dazhao, styled Shouchang, Director of Peking University Library]

74
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:06,320
because I want to know about your views on this.

75
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,280
Should I leave Beijing?

76
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:13,280
The situation I'm facing at the moment is rather urgent.

77
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,400
The police

78
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:17,040
has set a surveillance post right at my door.

79
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:19,040
Seconds after I arrived at my house,

80
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:22,000
Wu Bingxiang came to warn me,

81
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,760
that I can not leave Beijing without permission.

82
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,160
Now I am clearly targeted.

83
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,240
That's a tricky situation indeed.

84
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:32,080
I should probably just leave for safety.

85
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,880
But I was wondering that if I leave,

86
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,400
what would happen to "New Youth"?

87
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,120
After all, it's not my business alone.

88
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,360
This Wu Bingxiang is really shameless.

89
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,280
I say just ignore him.

90
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,440
He can't put you back in jail just for that.

91
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,880
Where is the law and regulation then?

92
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,920
There is no such thing as being too cautious.

93
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,040
People like Wu Bingxiang,

94
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,480
they can do everything.

95
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,240
Law and regulations are not gonna stop him.

96
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,640
Zhongfu, you should pay more attention anyway.

97
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,160
I read the Wuhan newspaper

98
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,440
and the remarks that appeared in your speech.

99
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,520
You openly publicized communism,

100
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,960
theory of class struggle.

101
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,040
You also mentioned revolution with bloodshed,

102
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,560
demolishing private ownership.

103
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,720
These remarks are really out of line.

104
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,480
Of course they would go after you.

105
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,560
Why can't you learn your lessons?

106
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,360
Shizhi, is it even meaningful to say this now?

107
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,080
If you ask me, why not go to the South?

108
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,160
Go to the South and start your fight there.

109
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:19,920
The South?

110
00:05:20,516 --> 00:05:21,760
Zhongfu just barely

111
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,560
escaped from Wuhan.

112
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,480
Shizhi, now we have to go to the South.

113
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,040
Or...

114
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,160
Sorry, guys.

115
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:27,840
I'm sorry.

116
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,080
I got everyone involved.

117
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:35,760
Well, I think I'd better leave Beijing.

118
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,280
Chinese New Year is coming soon.

119
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,440
If something really happens to me,

120
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,520
everyone is not gonna enjoy and relax during this time.

121
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,360
Brother Zhongfu, where are you going?

122
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:48,640
I'm thinking accept the offer to teach in Southwest University

123
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,280
from the Southern Government.

124
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,440
I want to go to Shanghai first.

125
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:56,080
The political environment there is better than that in Beijing.

126
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,800
Plus the labor and business communities have been exposed to the new ideology for a long time.

127
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,920
Unlike Beijing, all those happened were only in student groups.

128
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,880
In addition, I also want to bring "New Youth"

129
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,840
to Shanghai,

130
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:10,080
if you here will agree with that.

131
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,560
In Beijing,

132
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,840
especially in Peking University,

133
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,120
"New Youth" has already built a solid base.

134
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:18,160
Why start from the beginning in a different place?

135
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,000
I agree with brother Zhongfu.

136
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,760
The "New Youth" was brought by Zhongfu.

137
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,360
Naturally, it should follow you.

138
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,280
"New Youth" is not "New Youth" without Chen Duxiu.

139
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,400
No matter where it goes,

140
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,680
where it stays,

141
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,440
as long as brother Zhongfu is taking care of it,

142
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,760
we will support as always.

143
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:32,480
I agree.

144
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,280
I agree.

145
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,400
Thank you Yucai.

146
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,480
Then it's settled.

147
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,360
I will go to Shanghai by train tomorrow.

148
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,280
After arriving in Shanghai,

149
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:46,640
I'll ask Zhang Shizhao in the name of the Southern Government

150
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:49,120
to send an official letter to the Metropolitan Police Department first thing,

151
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,720
informing them that I accepted the job

152
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,800
as the organizer of Southwest University.

153
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,480
Then everyone will be out of trouble.

154
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,880
Besides, after arriving in Shanghai,

155
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,560
I will finish the next issue

156
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,760
of "New Youth".

157
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,840
Things after that, we will discuss another time.

158
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:04,720
Sure, it seems like the safest way now.

159
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,320
Director.

160
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:10,000
Our people went to Jiangan Hutong again just now.

161
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,600
Chen Duxiu was not home.

162
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,520
Looks like he went to drink with some friends.

163
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,560
Drinking?

164
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,400
Who did he go drinking with?

165
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,040
This better not be causing trouble.

166
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,320
Indeed.

167
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,400
I say we just arrest him.

168
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,760
Come back, come back.

169
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,600
You have to stop this.

170
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,320
Always acting without thinking.

171
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,200
Think about the grand scheme now.

172
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,880
The North-South Peace Period.

173
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,040
I heard that Chen Jiongming even invited him out,

174
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:45,360
offering him a job as the organizer of Southwest University.

175
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:48,720
If we act rashly at this time,

176
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,280
arrest him,

177
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:52,000
will the Southern Government just sit and do nothing?

178
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,440
Director!

179
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,520
It's Chinese New Year soon.

180
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,800
Chen Duxiu is a potential danger of public security in Beijing.

181
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,800
Look at his speech in Wuhan.

182
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,400
Aggresive and inflammatory.

183
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,080
That can possibly cause a lot of damage.

184
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,600
I understand what you said.

185
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,120
You know what?

186
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:10,640
Send someone to invite him to the hall tomorrow.

187
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,160
Ask him to write a guarantee.

188
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,000
If he agrees to our terms,

189
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,440
then let him go back.

190
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:18,240
If he doesn't agree, then detain him.

191
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,840
Make it acceptable for the public.

192
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:21,680
Tomorrow.

193
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:22,720
Tomorrow.

194
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,320
Got it.

195
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:25,680
I'll arrange it.

196
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,320
Good.

197
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,800
Zhongfu.

198
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,080
Mrs. Chen.

199
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,200
You are all here.

200
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,320
Zhongfu.

201
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:55,040
The police went to the house to look for you just now.

202
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,320
I told them

203
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,760
that you went to a friend's place for a drink.

204
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,200
They left without saying anything.

205
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,880
But I'm worried

206
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,800
they might come again later.

207
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,600
I think you should go hide now.

208
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,720
I saw that coming.

209
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,120
Sister-in-law, don't worry.

210
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,600
Brother Zhongfu can stay here tonight.

211
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,040
I'll even say Wu Bingxiang

212
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,560
will not dare to just come here and arrest people.

213
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,360
Shizhi, Zhongfu can't stay with you.

214
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,880
You are one of the sponsors.

215
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:23,040
Wu Bingxiang is likely to come here looking for him.

216
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,440
I say you stay at my place tonight.

217
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,080
Besides, you can't take the train

218
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,600
departing from Beijing to Shanghai tomorrow.

219
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,360
The police will be waiting.

220
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,720
They won't let you go.

221
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,080
I'll take you,

222
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,160
we go to Tianjin and you leave to Shanghai there.

223
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:37,840
Ok.

224
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,680
We need to move fast.

225
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,880
Brother Zhongfu.

226
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,000
After today's farewell,

227
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,600
I don't know when I will see you again.

228
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,680
Wait for me. I'll get the wine.

229
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,120
Good one, Hua Diao wine.

230
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,080
The kind you had before.

231
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,760
Deqian, we don't have time now.

232
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,600
I will run, we can make it.

233
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,400
Deqian.

234
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,760
I have Hua Diao at home.

235
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,000
Yeah, yeah, Hua Diao wine.

236
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,560
Can't have it cold.

237
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,760
Bad for health.

238
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,200
I'll heat it up.

239
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,720
Don't worry.

240
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,280
Wine might be cold, but our blood is hot.

241
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,640
Come on.

242
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,360
Come.

243
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,320
Guys!

244
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:41,280
I came to Beijing at the beginning of 1917.

245
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,960
Originally just helping Cai Yuanpei out

246
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,280
for only three months.

247
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:48,320
I didn't expect that three months turned into three years.

248
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,680
These three years,

249
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:52,240
from starting "New Youth" by myself

250
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,720
to have so many fellow brothers.

251
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,320
We built a career together.

252
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,560
We set up a banner together.

253
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,680
I have no regrets and no shame at these past three years.

254
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,320
This cup of wine

255
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:08,240
has the respect of all fellow brothers' love for me.

256
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,880
Junman, have it with me.

257
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:31,040
Brother Zhongfu, do you still remember a few years ago

258
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,960
when we met each other at Tao Ran Temple?

259
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,200
How can I forget that?

260
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,600
You warmed up the wine at home,

261
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,480
you were afraid of it getting cold,

262
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:46,080
so you wrapped it in a quilt, rented a rickshaw,

263
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:49,120
and brought it all the way in that freezing day.

264
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,920
We had hot Hua Diao wine in that snowy winter.

265
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:55,360
No one will do that again I guess.

266
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,880
This wine is a little cold today.

267
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:04,080
Brother Zhongfu, I used my hands to warm it up a little.

268
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,840
Have this one instead.

269
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,800
This will do.

270
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,640
Now in my chest,

271
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,600
I have a warm fire lightening up.

272
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:21,120
You, snow and Hua Diao wine,

273
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,560
isn't this the same as that day?

274
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,360
The same indeed.

275
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:26,880
We had our start, now we have our end.

276
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,680
Brother Zhongfu, you are my friend forever.

